log in
ssh mmagno@euler.ethz.ch


Load python and compyler, install repo and set up virtual env:
module load gcc/6.3.0 python/3.8.5
python -m venv --system-site-packages myenv
source myenv/bin/activate
git clone https://github.com/advilema/safe_multiagent_RL.git
cd safe_multiagent_RL
pip install -r requirements.txt
pip install --upgrade pip


Download directory:
scp -r mmagno@euler.ethz.ch:safe_multiagent_RL/results .
(instead of mmagno put your username)

Run experiments on Git Bash (submit the job):
bsub -n 1 -W 6:00 bash ./marco_experiments1.bat (submit the job)
bash ./marco_experiments.bat (run from terminal)

Activate virtual environment:
source myenv/bin/activate

Monitor jobs:
bjobs (pending jobs -p, running jobs -r)

kill job:
bkill [job ID]
